Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.37,0:01:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Mr. Ryu, standby okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, standby for docking.\NReady?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going in, Mr. Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,5... 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2... 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser searcher synchronized.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,5... 4...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.43,0:01:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam B Parts released!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Core Change! Docking, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The young crew had survived thus far\Nby working together as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But selfishness and frustration...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...had created an uncomfortable tension\Namong the crew members.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...the enemy was bearing down on them\Nregardless of the youths' problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.39,0:02:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand-to-Hand Combat
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The decryption isn't wrong, is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It says,\N"Don't move until Odessa Day."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:03:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll get us at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but Marker and Oscar\Nneed to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Those two may be\Nthe hardest workers in the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I join you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you mending the kids' clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm all finished.\N- You're such a busy bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you eating at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Close the door. I might escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That Ramba Ral guy\Nwill definitely come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.38,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without his Zakus and Gouf...\Nhe'll be all the more determined. For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So let 'em come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pilot the Gundam then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I might leave the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Why shouldn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No one feels comfortable with me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You put all your strength into that punch,\Ndidn't you, Mr. Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a time when\NMs. Matilda said that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...might be some kind of an Esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a reasonable thing\Nto say about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time you stopped sulking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Quoting Ms. Matilda?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Try lecturing me with your own words.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Fraw Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he really think one angry man\Nis enough to change a person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about Amuro, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.06,0:04:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...Mr. Bright, you have no intention\Nof taking him off the Gundam, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you put him in the brig...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...is to make Amuro think about what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're still counting on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But Bright, you were the one\Nwho wanted to remove him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro could have taken the Gundam\Nand defected to Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I puzzled over why he didn't do that.\NAnd as a result, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:05:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- Have hopes for him?\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro only came back because\Nhe was momentarily homesick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, he's almost\Nwhere we need him to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Ryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this about Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...\NI think he'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.54,0:05:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Ral,\Na message from Admiral Dozle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was relayed by Captain M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is good news, Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sending us 3 ground type\NDom mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Doms?\NYou mean those heavy mobile suits?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.84,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamon, we're moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We attack the Trojan Horse\Nas soon as we receive the Doms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the command of Kycilia Zabi,\NCaptain M'Quve's unit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...controls the world's largest\Nmineral resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is M'Quve's main base.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral knows too much\Nabout my mining activities here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,These mines will be useful when\NLady Kycilia rules Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Lord Gihren\Ncannot realize the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, sir.\N- You know what to do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But... we're sabotaging a request\Nfrom the Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NRamba Ral won't see it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.93,0:06:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryu! Wake up! Ryu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ryu! Hayato and the others just left!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, Ms. Sayla?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato, Kai, Howard, and Maximilian\Njust took off! Can you follow them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure, I'll get right on It!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this!\NEveryone's acting so selfishly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me! I'll bring them back\Neven if I've gotta knock some sense into them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu! I want to go too! Take me with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato is pretty forthright,\Nin his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we really been paying\Ntoo much attention to Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's overlooking one crucial thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Overlooking what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When Amuro was away,\NI felt very uneasy as commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uneasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've brought us a lot of luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...but without Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...I felt an incredible uneasiness\Nthat I've never felt before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Point A13. There's no mistake?\N- No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,30 minutes have passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, dear. A light!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That belongs to one of M'Quve's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Doms aren't coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It is very unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,M'Quve's forces couldn't provide\Ncover in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The supply ship was destroyed just before\Nentering Central Asia. The Doms were...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Lord M'Quve that I, Ramba Ral...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...will carry out my mission,\Neven if it's with my bare hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.\N- Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's what they mean\Nby "stubborn old war-horse".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as you predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't rely on reinforcements, so we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll use my old specialty, guerrilla tactics.\NWhat do you think, Clamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The men would love it, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they finally stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you guys think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to be\Non the White Base to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll find a local Federation unit and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to abandon Bright?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bright has Amuro with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lost my reason to fight\Naboard the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing anyone can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gallop goes in front of the Trojan Horse\Nand acts as a decoy, with Ghien's Zaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we come in from behind with the Cuis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamon will take command of the Gallop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Clamp and I will command\Nthe first and second Cuis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- Got that?\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Mobilize the Gallop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When we see the Trojan Horse, the Zaku\Nand Cuis will split off from the Gallop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Trojan Horse.\NIt's only moved 10 kilometers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaku! Cuis! Prepare to launch from\Nthe Gallop in 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can escape once we're on\Nthe Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.45,0:10:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You be careful too, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to hit me, Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't force people to listen to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys won't understand unless you're hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's that sound?\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down! We can't let them spot us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That sound...\NMust be the Gallop the prisoner mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's headed for the White Base.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to ask your own conscience\Nwhether you'll come back or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Ryu!\N- Well, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaku, Ghien, launch!\NFollowed by the Cuis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are we going?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that all right?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure got chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Kai...?\N- Huh? Oh, fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This wind, this sensation...\NThis is war!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the pilot\Nof that white mobile suit, Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a nice boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how he fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla! How close are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get an accurate estimate\Nat this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've called for Oscar and Marker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare forward missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.18,0:13:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai! Get the power up on the main engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. Engine start, complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,1 minute 20 seconds\Nuntil we can resume flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we slept in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Open beam cannons on both sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The rear missiles too.\NThere's more than one enemy machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! Open beam cannons!\NAssessing the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Something in front of us.\NPossibly the Gallop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't see anything else due to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can the White Base ascend, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet! Open forward observation camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Gallop! Entering firing range!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire main cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.12,0:14:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Port-side guns!\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Zaku! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bright, I'm launching In the Gundam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sayla...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Zaku on the left. Get some altitude\Nso you won't be a sitting duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best. Gundam, launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow, get Amuro out of the brig.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The door key is type 6E.\NDo you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the White Base's buggies are driving\Nall the way over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't do anything over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Have Ryu and the others come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there! You can see them, Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirai! Bring the forward deck level with\Nthe mountain ledge on the starboard side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Fraw Bow!\N- Amuro! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.42,0:15:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- The Gundam?\N- Ms. Sayla took it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're manning the port-side machine guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right!\N- Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the hell are those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- Looks like tanks...\N- You're right! Those are for commandos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're planning to storm us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're jumping onto the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The buggies made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Two tanks from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Commando tanks, called Cuis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Commandos?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I took so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! Get further back before you aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Ms. Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse is going to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being attacked from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu! Kai! Anyone who can fight,\Ngo to the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to halt the enemy's advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Marker! Oscar! Do you have sidearms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless they're trying to capture\Nthe White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Gallop would be hitting us harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That man is coming...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Charge in where there's not as much fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Clamp team, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them into the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam's weapons are too powerful...\Nthere's no way I can hit just the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.64,0:17:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk! Go away! I hope you fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.83,0:17:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What's a little kid doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:18:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back! Or you'll get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you to get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oscar and Marker! Take the bridge entrance!\NJob John! To the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatch 78 has been breached!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! We're taking the sub-bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were armed, I'd kill you!\NGo hide somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The man from the restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You won because of that mobile suit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not because of your own strength!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Replace Sayla in the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the Gundam to get the enemy\Nout of the second bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, even if the White Base takes damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you, Amuro!\N- Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where's the enemy?!\N- The second bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's kind of strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...that they're all child soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.93,0:19:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're all short of personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's here! The enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Go straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the main bridge control circuits!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really you, Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain of it. You must be Lady Artesia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My father served under your father,\NLord Zeon Deikun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ramba Ral, son of Jimba Ral!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know that I'm Artesia...\Nwhy do you point that gun at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What...? Then... what are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla! Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, can you hear me?!\NThey've taken the second bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.54,0:20:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,C... Contact Hamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! I have the frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You men retreat. The mission's a failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear... ?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy the Trojan Horse with the Gallop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of a fight,\NRamba Ral forgot to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.15,0:21:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lady Artesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's happened?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that mobile suit, Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that my opponents\Nwere all less than half my age...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You have fought splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.54,0:21:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But now you'll see the fate of a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ral...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Hamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.65,0:22:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eject the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Still nothing from the lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.87,0:22:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.51,0:22:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramba Ral...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And Hamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.89,0:23:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Carry him carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.58,0:23:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamon carries on the objective\Nof the fallen warrior, Ramba Ral.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.51,0:23:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,With so few weapons at her disposal...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...will Hamon be the one\Nto finally bring down Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.97,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In the midst of this crisis,\NRyu Jose's Core Fighter appears...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...to attack Hamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NSorrow and Hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorrow and Hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.68,0:23:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:54.36,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:59.37,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:09.59,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:14.51,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:19.14,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:24.52,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:29.11,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:39.41,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.52,0:23:54.36,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.36,0:23:59.37,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:09.59,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.59,0:24:14.51,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:19.14,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:24.52,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:29.11,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.11,0:24:39.41,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
